txt.en: Kindred to the March on Gundabad
You have proven yourself invaluable to the March on Gundabad and have done much to aid those in Elderslade. For this, the March on Gundabad now count you among their own.
You must earn Kindred standing with the March on Gundabad
The March on Gundabad count you among their own, and your deeds will be remembered for ages to come.
